    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307020/extras/812cb157269f4149c10799e64205ffa4.avif?t=1770260273\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307020/extras_big/812cb157269f4149c10799e64205ffa4.avif?t=1770260273 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Wake up in a temple.</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the ancient temple, acquire powerful artifacts, but beware of dangers!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Unique puzzle-solving.</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the amulet's powerful magic to help you solve puzzles.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Uncover the truth.</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Where am I, how did I get here? The answers lie within the void.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307020/extras/e5162a0703b62704e8724c72b6e68039.avif?t=1770260273\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307020/extras_big/e5162a0703b62704e8724c72b6e68039.avif?t=1770260273 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game is created by <strong>@Reset</strong> with YAHAHA Horror Game Kit and YAHAHA assists the creator with packaging and publishing the game based on their request. Yahaha Horror Gamekit is tailored for imaginative creators and players who adore horror games, all without the need for any programming expertise.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307020/extras/29e17dc2ac92b9f72fe64019e1839073.avif?t=1770260273\" width=720 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
